item.dc:creator: @MasterElite MasterElite
item.description:
@MasterElite wrote:

Exactly as he said, so open ‘Server.java’ Then CTRL+F ‘3334’ and where it says:

public static int serverlistenerPort = 3334; //43594=default

Replace the 3334 with another port don’t replace the default though. Then compile the server. Then you are done.
